  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Half-board meals taken in the Tobelm<span>ühlesaal dining hall</span></p>
<p>Each morning a varied buffet breakfast with a daily hot options including eggs, bacon, sausages or pancakes is served, as well as the classic continental offering. You can also enjoy complimentary tree and cake when you return from the slopes. </p>
<p>Dinner includes a four course evening meal with choice of set starter or soup, salad buffet, two main options and set dessert or fresh fruit. Early meal times for children from 6pm (available on request)</p>
<p>The lovely Piano Bar serves drinks and snacks throughout the day until late evening.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included. New Year gala dinner is 6 courses with choice of 2 music and dancing venues in-house, followed by New Year's day brunch on 1st January</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
