  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard West Rooms</strong> are about 25m² and sleep two people. The beds are swiss style with two separate single mattresses. They have a bath or shower and a balcony. These rooms are also available for single use. </p>
<p><strong>Superior West</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> are about 25m² and sleep two people. The beds are swiss style with two separate single mattresses. These renovated are furnished and decorated in an elegant, alpine style and have a shower and a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong>  can sleep three adults or two adults and two children (double sofa bed), these rooms also have a balcony. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Bathrobe (on request)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
